data.name: grdReserOrderList.QuerySQL
data.value: -- OCS_FLAG(登録[1],予約[2],実施[3]) SELECT KIZYUN_DATE , GWA , GWA_NAME , DOCTOR , DOCTOR_NAME , HANGMOG_CODE , HANGMOG_NAME , JUNDAL_TABLE , JUNDAL_PART , JUNDAL_PART_NAME , RESER_TIME , RESER_YN , ACT_YN , ORDER_DATE , PKSCH FROM( /* SELECT A.ORDER_DATE AS KIZYUN_DATE , A.GWA AS GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.ORDER_DATE) AS GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR AS DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) AS DOCTOR_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE AS HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME AS HANGMOG_NAME , A.JUNDAL_TABLE AS JUNDAL_TABLE , A.JUNDAL_PART AS JUNDAL_PART , C.BUSEO_NAME AS JUNDAL_PART_NAME , A.RESER_TIME AS RESER_TIME , 'A' AS RESER_YN , DECODE(A.OCS_FLAG, '1', 'N', '2', 'N', 'Y') AS ACT_YN , A.ORDER_DATE AS ORDER_DATE , 0 AS PKSCH FROM OCS1003 A , OCS0103 B , BAS0260 C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_naewon_date AND A.HOPE_DATE IS NULL AND A.OCS_FLAG <> '2' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND REGEXP_LIKE (B.SLIP_CODE, 'B|E|G|J|M|N') -- B[検体],E[生理],G[放射],J[注射],M[処置],N[手術] AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.GWA = A.JUNDAL_PART AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND C.END_DATE UNION ALL */ SELECT A.RESER_DATE AS KIZYUN_DATE , A.GWA AS GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.INPUT_DATE) AS GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR AS DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) AS DOCTOR_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE AS HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME AS HANGMOG_NAME , A.JUNDAL_TABLE AS JUNDAL_TABLE , A.JUNDAL_PART AS JUNDAL_PART , C.JUNDAL_PART_NAME AS JUNDAL_PART_NAME , A.RESER_TIME AS RESER_TIME , DECODE(A.RESER_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') AS RESER_YN , DECODE(A.ACTING_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') AS ACT_YN , A.ORDER_DATE AS ORDER_DATE , A.PKSCH0201 AS PKSCH FROM SCH0201 A , OCS0103 B , SCH0001 C , OCS1003 D WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESER_DATE = :f_naewon_date AND A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.JUNDAL_TABLE <> 'PHY' AND NVL(A.CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.JUNDAL_TABLE = A.JUNDAL_TABLE AND C.JUNDAL_PART = A.JUNDAL_PART -- AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.PKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS AND ( (NVL(D.INSTEAD_YN, 'N') = 'N') OR (NVL(D.INSTEAD_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL(D.APPROVE_YN, 'N') = 'Y') ) UNION ALL SELECT B.RESER_DATE AS KIZYUN_DATE , A.GWA AS GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, B.RESER_DATE) AS GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR AS DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, B.RESER_DATE) AS DOCTOR_NAME , B.HANGMOG_CODE AS HANGMOG_CODE , C.HANGMOG_NAME AS HANGMOG_NAME , 'INJ' AS JUNDAL_TABLE , A.JUNDAL_PART AS JUNDAL_PART , D.BUSEO_NAME AS JUNDAL_PART_NAME , B.RESER_TIME AS RESER_TIME , DECODE(B.RESER_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') AS RESER_YN , DECODE(B.ACTING_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') AS ACT_YN , A.ORDER_DATE AS ORDER_DATE , B.PKINJ1002 AS PKSCH FROM BAS0260 D , OCS0103 C , INJ1002 B , INJ1001 A , OCS1003 E WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.FKINJ1001 = A.PKINJ1001 AND A.ORDER_DATE <> B.RESER_DATE AND B.RESER_DATE = :f_naewon_date AND NVL(B.DC_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = B.HANGMOG_CODE AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND C.END_DATE AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.GWA = A.JUNDAL_PART AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN D.START_DATE AND D.END_DATE -- AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.PKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003 AND ( (NVL(E.INSTEAD_YN, 'N') = 'N') OR (NVL(E.INSTEAD_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND NVL(E.APPROVE_YN, 'N') = 'Y') ) ) ORDER BY KIZYUN_DATE, ORDER_DATE, GWA, DOCTOR, JUNDAL_TABLE, JUNDAL_PART, RESER_TIME NULLS FIRST, RESER_YN

data.name: grdOutSang.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.BUNHO , A.GWA --insert by jc , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, SYSDATE) GWA_NAME , A.IO_GUBUN , A.PK_SEQ , A.NAEWON_DATE , A.JUBSU_NO , A.LAST_NAEWON_DATE , A.LAST_DOCTOR , A.LAST_NAEWON_TYPE , A.LAST_JUBSU_NO , A.FKOUT1001 , A.FKINP1001 , A.INPUT_ID , A.SER , A.SANG_CODE , A.JU_SANG_YN , A.SANG_NAME , A.PRE_MODIFIER_NAME || A.SANG_NAME || A.POST_MODIFIER_NAME , A.SANG_START_DATE , A.SANG_END_DATE , A.SANG_END_SAYU , A.PRE_MODIFIER1 , A.PRE_MODIFIER2 , A.PRE_MODIFIER3 , A.PRE_MODIFIER4 , A.PRE_MODIFIER5 , A.PRE_MODIFIER6 , A.PRE_MODIFIER7 , A.PRE_MODIFIER8 , A.PRE_MODIFIER9 , A.PRE_MODIFIER10 , A.PRE_MODIFIER_NAME , A.POST_MODIFIER1 , A.POST_MODIFIER2 , A.POST_MODIFIER3 , A.POST_MODIFIER4 , A.POST_MODIFIER5 , A.POST_MODIFIER6 , A.POST_MODIFIER7 , A.POST_MODIFIER8 , A.POST_MODIFIER9 , A.POST_MODIFIER10 , A.POST_MODIFIER_NAME , A.SANG_JINDAN_DATE , A.PKOUTSANG , A.DATA_GUBUN , A.IF_DATA_SEND_YN , ( CASE WHEN A.JU_SANG_YN = 'Y' THEN '0' ELSE '1' END )|| ( CASE WHEN A.SANG_END_DATE IS NULL THEN '0' ELSE '1' END )|| /* 疑い病名が上に表示されない様に注釈処理 ( CASE WHEN NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER1 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER2 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER3 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER4 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER5 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER6 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER7 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER8 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER9 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER10, 'XXXX') = '8002' THEN '0' ELSE '1' END )|| */ TO_CHAR(A.SANG_START_DATE, 'YYYYMMDD')||LTRIM(TO_CHAR(A.SER, '0000000000')) ORDER_BY_KEY FROM OUTSANG A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.GWA LIKE :f_gwa AND A.IO_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.SANG_START_DATE <= TO_DATE(:f_naewon_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND NVL(A.SANG_END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) >= TO_DATE(:f_naewon_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.DATA_GUBUN != 'D' ORDER BY ORDER_BY_KEY

data.name: cboQryGwa.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '%', FN_ADM_MSG(221) FROM SYS.DUAL UNION ALL SELECT A.GWA, A.GWA_NAME FROM BAS0260 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.BUSEO_GUBUN = '1' AND A.OUT_JUBSU_YN = 'Y' AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND NVL(A.END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) AND A.GWA IS NOT NULL ORDER BY 1

data.value:
SELECT A.BUNHO , A.NAEWON_DATE , A.GWA , A.DOCTOR , A.NAEWON_TYPE , NVL(A.RESER_YN, 'N') RESER_YN -- , NVL(A.ARRIVE_TIME, A.JUBSU_TIME) JUBSU_TIME , A.JUBSU_TIME JUBSU_TIME , A.ARRIVE_TIME ARRIVE_TIME , DECODE(A.NAEWON_YN ,'H', '['||FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('NAEWON_YN', A.NAEWON_YN)||'] ' , '') || B.SUNAME SUNAME , B.SUNAME2 , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME( 'SEX', B.SEX ) SEX , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE ( A.NAEWON_DATE, B.BIRTH, 'XXXX') AGE , FN_BAS_LOAD_GUBUN_NAME ( A.GUBUN, A.NAEWON_DATE ) GUBUN_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME ( A.GWA, A.NAEWON_DATE ) GWA_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME ( A.DOCTOR, A.NAEWON_DATE ) DOCTOR_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME ( 'CHOJAE', A.CHOJAE ) CHOJAE_NAME , CASE WHEN (A.NAEWON_YN = 'E') THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END JINRYO_END_YN , A.PKOUT1001 PK_NAEWON , A.NAEWON_YN NAEWON_YN , A.SUNNAB_YN SUNNAB_YN , A.JUBSU_GUBUN JUBSU_GUBUN , CASE WHEN (FN_OCS_LOAD_TA_GWA_JINRYO_CNT ( A.BUNHO, A.NAEWON_DATE, A.GWA ) > 0) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END OTHER_GWA , CASE WHEN (C.PKOCS0503 IS NULL) THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END CONSULT_YN , A.JUBSU_GUBUN JUBSU_GUBUN , NVL(D.COMMON_DOCTOR_YN , 'N') COMMON_DOCTOR_YN , A.GUBUN GUBUN , NVL(E.GROUP_KEY, '0') GROUP_KEY , A.KENSA_YN KENSA_YN , DECODE(FN_OCS_GET_NOTAPPROVE_ORDERCNT(A.HOSP_CODE, 'O', 'Y', 'N', SUBSTR(A.DOCTOR, LENGTH(A.DOCTOR) -4), A.PKOUT1001), 0, 'N', 'Y') UNAPPROVE_YN FROM BAS0102 E , BAS0270 D , OCS0503 C , OUT0101 B , OUT1001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NAEWON_DATE = :f_naewon_date
--診療科関係なくドクター宛に受付された患者さんみんな表示させるように変更。2013/02/10 -- AND A.GWA = :f_gwa AND A.NAEWON_YN IN ('Y', 'E', 'H') -- 내원확인된 환자. AND CASE WHEN (A.NAEWON_YN IN ('E', 'H')) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END LIKE :f_naewon_yn AND NVL(A.RESER_YN, 'N') LIKE :f_reser_yn AND ( ( :f_doctor_mode_yn = 'Y' AND ( A.DOCTOR LIKE '%'||SUBSTR(:f_doctor, 3) --診療科関係なくドクター宛に受付された患者さんみんな表示させるように変更。2013/02/10 OR D.COMMON_DOCTOR_YN = 'Y' ) ) OR ( :f_doctor_mode_yn != 'Y' AND ( A.DOCTOR LIKE '%'||SUBSTR(:f_doctor, 3) ) ) ) -- AND A.NAEWON_TYPE != '1' -- 검사만의 환자인경우 내원타잎이 1로 저장될것임. AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho -- AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.CODE (+) = A.JUBSU_GUBUN AND E.CODE_TYPE (+) = 'JUBSU_GUBUN' -- AND NVL(E.GROUP_KEY, '0') = '1' AND ( (:f_doctor_mode_yn = 'Y' AND NVL(E.GROUP_KEY, '0') = '1') OR :f_doctor_mode_yn != 'Y') -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO -- AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.CONSULT_FKOUT1001 (+) = A.PKOUT1001 -- AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.DOCTOR = A.DOCTOR AND A.NAEWON_DATE BETWEEN D.START_DATE AND D.END_DATE ORDER BY NVL(A.ARRIVE_TIME, A.JUBSU_TIME), A.BUNHO, A.JUBSU_NO
